  "detailed_description": "A relaxing simulator for lovers of the Middle Ages and nature. You play the role of a medieval baker who has to earn coins, improve his own farm, harvest wheat, grind grain, chop wood and bake. Learn a lot of recipes, improving your character's skills. You will need to monitor the performance of your hero and restore them in time.<br><br>The economy of the game will force you to interact with several merchants and take short cuts.<br><br>Additional medieval board games await you in the small tavern.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/244aeb0b8fe60dc41990486a47b10e06.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/0516fb29defe5a54056bcd7716c1ca3c.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/8bd9585c2fea59057e4d993c1c098da0.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Small cozy open world<br></li><li> 100+ recipes<br></li><li> Building constructions<br></li><li> 3 mini-games in the tavern<br></li><li> Unique graphics<br></li><li> Atmosphere of nature<br></li><li> Author's soundtracks from the developer</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the game \"<i>Medieval simulators: Baker</i>\" and enjoy the game. :)</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/17ce0db5de938af5beb99fb6eb02fbb2.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A relaxing simulator for lovers of the Middle Ages and nature. You play the role of a medieval baker who has to earn coins, improve his own farm, harvest wheat, grind grain, chop wood and bake. Learn a lot of recipes, improving your character's skills. You will need to monitor the performance of your hero and restore them in time.<br><br>The economy of the game will force you to interact with several merchants and take short cuts.<br><br>Additional medieval board games await you in the small tavern.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/244aeb0b8fe60dc41990486a47b10e06.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/0516fb29defe5a54056bcd7716c1ca3c.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/8bd9585c2fea59057e4d993c1c098da0.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Small cozy open world<br></li><li> 100+ recipes<br></li><li> Building constructions<br></li><li> 3 mini-games in the tavern<br></li><li> Unique graphics<br></li><li> Atmosphere of nature<br></li><li> Author's soundtracks from the developer</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the game \"<i>Medieval simulators: Baker</i>\" and enjoy the game. :)</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392690/extras/17ce0db5de938af5beb99fb6eb02fbb2.avif?t=1769420428\" width=616 height=308 /></span>",
